This paper deals with collaborative decision making in multi-agent systems, which is a core topic in the field of multi-agent systems (MAS). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also discusses learning an efficient communication protocol, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (AI), making cs.AI a likely category as well. The paper uses an actor-critic scheme, which is a popular reinforcement learning technique, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with taking action in a distributed manner, which is a common topic in the field of robotics (RO), making cs.RO a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with achieving a common goal/task, which is a common topic in the field of control systems (SY), making cs.SY a possible category.
